author: PlayStation
description:
https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10012908

Code Violet: Survive the Horror, Unravel the Truth.  Join Violet Sinclair in Code Violet, a pulse-pounding third-person action horror game on PS5 in 2025. Torn from your time to a 25th-century colony on Trappist 1-E, battle ferocious dinosaurs and uncover a sinister conspiracy in the Aion Bioengineering Complex. With scarce resources, strategic inventory management, and explosive combat, outmaneuver prehistoric beasts and hostile forces. Immerse yourself in stunning ray-traced visuals, Sony’s 3D audio, and haptic feedback, solving mind-bending puzzles to escape a chaotic evacuation. Can you survive and expose Aion’s dark secrets?

#ps5 #ps5games 

Rated Mature
